Test Case ID: TC-013

Title:
Verify locked out user cannot access the application

Preconditions:
1. User is on the Sauce Demo login page.
2. User has a valid username and password.

Test Steps:
1. Enter "locked_out_user" into the Username field.
2. Enter "secret_sauce" into the Password field.
3. Click the Login button.

Expected Result:
1. User remains on the login page.
2. User is not authenticated.
3. Access to the Inventory page is denied.
4. Error message "Epic sadface: Sorry, this user has been locked out." is displayed.
